{
  "stem": "3382.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] One day, beginning of July, Rachela came.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They took away her husband, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they threw her out from her apartment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I have to tell you that Rachela married in a very wealthy family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And her husband-- the family was one of richest in Vilna.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And everybody knew them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she was hated by Poles and Lithuanians, you know. 'Rich kikes' is what they'd called them, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So Rachela had no place to go, so she came to live there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this how we became closer, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "By the way, let me tell you one thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When the Germans came, and I couldn't get maternity clothes-- not the Germans-- when, when the Soviets came.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So Rachela gave Sula, my wife, her maternity clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then we became, you know, very friendly, you know, real friends, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And anyway, so I used to go across the city, sometimes zigzagging.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But in one place, I couldn't zigzag.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "This is when I crossed the River Vilnia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there one day, in the middle of July, on the corner of Kalvariska Street and Lwowska Street, I suddenly heard cries and shouts.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I turned to the left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I saw those Lithuanians-- we call them [NON-ENGLISH]; it means 'catchers,' you know-- drags a couple Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I decided to jump on the other side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I had to make one block, and then I went through number 49.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From number 49, would go to 51, where was the farm of my uncle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It means brother of my stepfather.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the corner was a big house-- a two-, three-story house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember, the owner was Baranowski.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, you know, that house had such gates-- had gates.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
